com.martinandersson.money.benchmark

Class ChronicleMapRealBenchmark

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.martinandersson.money.benchmark.ChronicleMapRealBenchmark

  • public class ChronicleMapRealBenchmark
extends java.lang.Object
    Benchmarks Chronicle Map using different serialization frameworks.

    The benchmark provided in this class work much like ChronicleMapBaselineBenchmark except that this class configure Chronicle Map to use a custom marshaller that delegate the serialization/deserialization to different serialization frameworks provided by SerializationFramework.

    On author's machine, the results of SerializationFramework.JAVA was almost [as expected] identical to ChronicleMapBaselineBenchmark.chronicleMap(Blackhole). One interested conclusion has to be that the act of using a custom marshaller has no notable impact.

    However, the other serialization frameworks vastly reduced the time cost. SerializationFramework.KRYO_CUSTOM was the fastest one and "only" 3.8 times slower than ChronicleMapBaselineBenchmark.concurrentHashMap(Blackhole).
